<% content_for :title, "Store Policy" %>

<%= render "page_hero",
  title: "Our Store Policy",
  subtitle: "Clear, fair, and customer-first — how we do business."
%>

<div class="container py-5">
  <div class="row g-5">
    <div class="col-12 col-lg-8">
      <p class="lead">
        At Prairie Naturals, we believe shopping should be simple, transparent, and worry-free.
        Our Store Policy is built around respect — for you, your time, your privacy, and the trust you place in us.
      </p>

      <h3 class="mt-4">How We Handle Your Orders</h3>
      <p>
        Every order is processed with care, typically within <strong>1–2 business days</strong>.
        You’ll always receive an email confirmation and tracking details so you can follow your purchase from our store to your door.
      </p>

      <h3 class="mt-4">Our Shipping Promise</h3>
      <p>
        We partner with reliable carriers to ensure your products arrive safely and on time.
        Standard and expedited shipping options are available, with costs and delivery times calculated at checkout.
      </p>

      <h3 class="mt-4">Returns & Exchanges</h3>
      <p>
        If you’re not fully satisfied, you can return most unopened items within <strong>30 days</strong> for a refund or exchange.
        Health and personal-care items may have additional restrictions — see our <%= link_to "full policies", storefront_policies_path %> for details.
      </p>

      <h3 class="mt-4">Your Privacy Matters</h3>
      <p>
        We treat your personal information with the same care we’d expect for our own.
        We never sell or trade your data, and we work with certified payment providers to protect your transactions.
        For more, read our <%= link_to "Privacy Policy", storefront_privacy_policy_path %>.
      </p>

      <h3 class="mt-4">Our Commitment to You</h3>
      <p>
        Quality is at the heart of everything we do. If something isn’t right with your order, contact us — we’ll make it right.
        Whether it’s a replacement, refund, or credit, we’ll work with you to find the best solution.
      </p>

      <div class="alert alert-light border mt-5">
        <p class="mb-1"><strong>Need More Details?</strong></p>
        <p class="mb-0">
          This page is a summary. You can view all specific rules and procedures in our
          <%= link_to "full policies here", storefront_policies_path, class: "fw-semibold" %>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Sidebar -->
    <div class="col-12 col-lg-4">
      <div class="border rounded-4 p-4 bg-light">
        <h4 class="h6 mb-3">Quick Links</h4>
        <ul class="list-unstyled small mb-0">
          <li><%= link_to "Privacy & Data", storefront_policies_path(anchor: "privacy") %></li>
          <li><%= link_to "Orders & Cancellations", storefront_policies_path(anchor: "orders") %></li>
          <li><%= link_to "Shipping & Returns", storefront_shipping_returns_path %></li>
          <li><%= link_to "Pricing & Promotions", storefront_policies_path(anchor: "pricing") %></li>
          <li><%= link_to "Quality Guarantee", storefront_policies_path(anchor: "quality") %></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="border rounded-4 p-4 mt-4">
        <h4 class="h6 mb-2">Questions?</h4>
        <p class="small mb-3">We usually reply within 1–2 business days.</p>
        <%= link_to "Contact Us", storefront_contact_path, class: "btn btn-dark btn-sm" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
